3920366067218393%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20post%20is%20nearly%20identical%20to%20the%20one%20he%20made%20on%20November%2030%2C%20weeks%20after%20winning%20the%202024%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRICS%20group%20-%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20and%20South%20Africa%20-%20has%20been%20discussing%20ways%20to%20reduce%20reliance%20on%20the%20US%20dollar%20for%20years.%20The%20BRICS%20economic%20collaboration%20has%20only%20intensified%20since%20Western%20sanctions%20were%20imposed%20on%20Russia%20following%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20BRICS%20has%20expanded%20to%20include%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BRICS%20does%20not%20have%20a%20common%20currency%2C%20its%20members%20have%20promoted%20trade%20in%20their%20local%20currencies.%20At%20the%2015th%20BRICS%20Summit%20in%202023%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20explicitly%20called%20for%20de-dollarisation%2C%20stating%20that%20BRICS%20nations%20%26quot%3Bmust%20expand%20settlements%20in%20national%20currencies%20and%20enhance%20cooperation%20between%20banks.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20gained%20further%20momentum%20at%20the%20June%202024%20BRICS%20foreign%20ministers'%20meeting%20in%20Russia%2C%20where%20member%20states%20advocated%20for%20using%20local%20currencies%20in%20bilateral%20and%20multilateral%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20over%20de-dollarisation%2C%20the%20US%20dollar%20remains%20the%20world's%20dominant%20reserve%20currency.%20A%20study%20by%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20GeoEconomics%20Center%20last%20year%20found%20that%20neither%20the%20euro%20nor%20BRICS%20nations%20had%20successfully%20reduced%20global%20reliance%20on%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20threats%20come%20as%20he%20seeks%20to%20maintain%20this%20dominance.%20His%20use%20of%20tariffs%20as%20leverage%20is%20not%20new.%20The%2078-year-old's%20threats%20against%20BRICS%20follow%20his%20recent%20push%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20the%20United%20States'%20largest%20trading%20partners.%20Trump%20has%20argued%20that%20such%20tariffs%20are%20necessary%20to%20combat%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20particularly%20fentanyl%2C%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20campaign%2C%20Trump%20called%20India%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20big%20abuser%26quot%3B%20of%20trade%20policies%20and%20has%20now%20extended%20similar%20rhetoric%20towards%20other%20BRICS%20members.%20He%20has%20argued%20that%20by%20increasing%20tariffs%20on%20other%20countries%2C%20he%20can%20lower%20taxes%20for%20American%20businesses%20and%20workers%2C%20bringing%20factories%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20met%20with%20scepticism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomists%20warn%20that%20tariffs%20could%20drive%20up%20costs%20for%20American%20consumers%20and%20businesses%2C%20particularly%20in%20industries%20that%20rely%20on%20imported%20raw%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738295940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjhgavsv_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_15_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-brics-dollar-seemingly-hostile-countries-donald-trump-threatens-brics-with-100-tariff-7600289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20issued%20a%20warning%20to%20BRICS%20nations%2C%20threatening%20100%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20their%20exports%20if%20they%20attempt%20to%20replace%20the%20US%20dollar%20as%20the%20dominant%20currency%20in%20international%20trade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JD%20Vance%20slams%20Selena%E2%80%99s%20immig