perated%20by%20American%20Airlines%20collided%20with%20a%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestigators%20on%20Thursday%20said%20they%20recovered%20the%20black%20boxes%20from%20the%20passenger%20jet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBlack%20boxes%20can%20provide%20key%20data%20from%20moments%20before%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20recovered%20the%20recording%20devices%2C%20or%20black%20boxes%2C%20from%20one%20of%20the%20aircraft%20involved%20in%20Wednesday%20night's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-subsidiary-plane-psa-crashes-potomac-river-dc-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emidair%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E%20near%20the%20Reagan%20Washington%20National%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%2C%20which%20is%20overseeing%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20crash%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcockpit%20voice%20recorder%20and%20flight%20data%20recorder%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Bombardier%20CRJ700%20airplane%20operated%20by%20American%20Airlines%20was%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recorders%20are%20at%20the%20NTSB%20labs%20for%20evaluation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairplane-black-box-explainer-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlack%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20their%20name%2C%20are%20actually%20bright%20orange.%20They%20provide%20key%20data%20that%20can%20help%20investigators%20determine%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20moments%20before%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cockpit%20voice%20recorder%20%26quot%3Brecords%20radio%20transmissions%20and%20sounds%20in%20the%20cockpit%2C%20such%20as%20the%20pilot's%20voices%20and%20engine%20noises%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20NTSB.%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%2C%20the%20Flight%20Data%20Recorder%20(FDR)