firmed%2C%20he%20would%20be%20the%20first%20Hindu%20and%20Indian%20American%20to%20be%20FBI%20Director.%20Patel%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20from%20Senator%20Lindsey%20Graham%20if%20he%20has%20ever%20been%20subject%20to%20racism%20as%20an%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20record%20from%20January%206th%2C%20where%20I%20testified%20before%20that%20committee%2C%20because%20of%20my%20personal%20information%20being%20released%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20a%20direct%20and%20significant%20threat%20on%20my%20life.%20And%20I%20put%20that%20information%20in%20the%20record.%20I%20had%20to%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20called%20a%20detestable%20--%20and%20I'll%20apologise%20if%20I%20don't%20get%20it%20all%20right%2C%20but%20it's%20in%20the%20record%20--%20a%20detestable%20sand%20nigger%20who%20had%20no%20right%20being%20in%20this%20country.%20You%20should%20go%20back%20to%20where%20you%20came%20from.%20You%20belong%20with%20your%20terrorist%20home%20friends.%20That's%20what%20was%20sent%20to%20me.%20That's%20just%20the%20piece%20of%20it%2C%20but%20that's%20nothing%20compared%20to%20what%20the%20men%20and%20women%20in%20law%20enforcement%20face%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20members%2C%20including%20his%20father%20and%20mother%2C%20who%20flew%20from%20India%2C%20were%20present%20at%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20during%20the%20confirmation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20be%20here%20today%20without%20their%20guidance%2C%20their%20unwavering%20support%2C%20and%20their%20relentless%20love.%20When%20President%20Trump%20informed%20me%20of%20his%20intention%20to%20nominate%20me%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20FBI%2C%20I%20was%20deeply%20honoured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSitting%20here%20today%2C%20I%20carry%20not%20only%20the%20dreams%20of%20my%20parents%20but%20also%20the%20hopes%20of%20millions%20of%20Americans%20who%20stand%20for%20justice%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20said%20his%20father%20fled%20Idi%20Amin's%20genocidal%20dictatorship%20in%20Uganda%2C%20where%20300%2C000%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20were%20killed%20based%20on%20their%20ethnicity%20just%20because%20they%20happened%20to%20look%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20is%20originally%20from%20Tanzania.%20She%20studied%20in%20India%2C%20as%20did%20my%20dad%2C%20and%20they%20were%20married%20there.%20They%20would%20later%20emigrate%20to%20New%20York%2C%20as%20the%20senator%20pointed%20out%2C%20where%20I%20was%20born%2C%20and%20we%20were%20raised%20in%20a%20household%20of%20my%20father's%20seven%20siblings%2C%20their%20spouses%2C%20and%20at%20least%20half%20a%20dozen%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20only%20way%20we%20knew%20how%20to%20do%20things%20at%20the%20time%2C%20in%20the%20'70s%20and%20'80s%2C%20the%20Indian%20way%2C%20but%20we%20would%20soon%20learn%20the%20American%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Thom%20Tillis%20said%20he%20is%20convinced%20that%20Patel%20possesses%20significant%20expertise%20and%20ironclad%20commitment%20to%20justice%20and%20he's%20an%20outstanding%20choice%20to%20lead%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKash's%20parents%20are%20Indian%20immigrants%20of%20Gujarati%20ancestry.%20They're%20up%20here%20in%20the%20front%20row.%20The%20Gujarat%20state%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20religions%2C%20including%20Hinduism%2C%20Islam%2C%20Jainism%2C%20with%20temples%2C%20mosques%20and%20other%20religious%20sites%20scattered%20across%20the%20state.%20His%20father%20was%20raised%20in%20Uganda%2C%20but%20his%20family%20had%20to%20flee%20the%20country%20to%20escape%20repression%20under%20Idi%20Amin.%20His%20mother%20was%20born%20in%20Tanzania%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20met%20and%20married%20in%20India%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20made%20their%20way%20to%20New%20York%20City%20by%20way%20of%20Canada%2C%20where%20his%20parents%20along%20with%20seven%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20and%20their%20spouses%20and%20at%20least%20a%20half%20a%20dozen%20kids%20lived%20under%20the%20same%20roof.%20His%20parents%20raised%20Kash%20in%20the%20Hindu%20faith%20and%20they%20instilled%20in%20him%20the%20values%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20Tellis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKash%20is%20a%20devout%20Hindu%2C%20and%20consistent%20with%20his%20faith%2C%20he's%20shown%20respect%20to%20people%20of%20all%20faiths%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Chuck%20Grassley%20said%20Patel's%20career%20has%20been%20a%20study%20in%20fighting%20unpopular%20but%20righteous%20causes%2C%20exposing%20corruption%2C%20and%20putting%20America%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20attacks%20on%20Patel%20by%20his%20opponents%20during%20his%20work%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20Grassley%20said%20Patel%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Ban%20enemies%20list%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20fair%20characterisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20added%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20revenge%20list.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMr%20Patel%20has%20identified%20those%20he%20believes%20have%20put%20politics%20and%20personal%20ambition%20over%20service%20to%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20called%20out%20those%20who've%20used%20the%20institutions%20like%20the%20FBI%20to%20achieve%20their%20own%20personal%20gain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Patel%20has%20said%20he%20believes%20that%20people%20who%20do%20this%20should%20be%20named%20and%20that%20Americans%20deserve%20transparency%20so%20that%20they%20can%20make%20their%20own%20judgement%2C%20as%20they%20did%20in%20this%20last%20election.%20Other%20attacks%20against%20Mr%20Patel%20are%20similarly%20unfounded%2C%26quo