%20be%20interpreted%20politically%2C%20responded%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20to%20a%20query%20by%20the%20media%20in%20Delhi%20after%20Mr%20Raut%20made%20the%20remark%20following%20an%20interaction%20between%20BJP%20leader%20Chandrakant%20Patil%20and%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20close%20aide%20Milind%20Narvekar%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut's%20comments%20came%20after%20Narvekar%2C%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Council%2C%20and%20Mr%20Patil%20had%20a%20few%20jovial%20exchanges%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Thackeray%20at%20the%20wedding%20reception%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Parag%20Alavani's%20daughter%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Alavani%20is%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20Vile%20Parle%20in%20suburban%20Mumbai.%20A%20BJP%20functionary%20said%20Thackeray%20shares%20cordial%20relations%20with%20Alavani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20attended%20the%20reception%20said%20Narvekar%20joked%20with%20Mr%20Patil%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20good%20that%20journalists%20are%20not%20here...otherwise%2C%20they%20would%20say%20alliance%20talks%20are%20on.%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Patil%20quipped%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20a%20golden%20moment.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CPatil%20belongs%20to%20the%20older%20generation%20of%20BJP%20who%20understands%20the%20significance%20of%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20ties.%20It%20worked%20well%20for%2025%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Raut%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20in%20the%20BJP%20share%20Mr%20Patil's%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20moment%E2%80%9D%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20Mr%20Raut's%20claims%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20told%20reporters%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20should%20be%20naive%20enough%20to%20think%20that%20just%20because%20people%20meet%20at%20a%20wedding%20(reception)%2C%20an%20alliance%20is%20formed%20or%20parties%20come%20closer.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Bal%20Thackeray-founded%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20BJP%20were%20partners%20for%2025%20years%20till%20the%20parties%20fell%20apart%20after%20the%202019%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%20over%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister.%20Then%20Sena%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20subsequently%20joined%20hands%20with%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20to%20become%20the%20CM%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MVA%20government%20fell%20in%202022%20after%20Shinde%20led%20a%20rebellion%20in%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20split%20the%20party.%20He%20later%20got%20the%20party%20name%20and%20its%20%E2%80%98bow%20and%20arrow'%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20leaders%20in%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20also%20share%20the%20same%20feeling%20of%20partnering%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Raut%20had%20said%20earlier%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20might%20be.%20We%20went%20with%20the%20MVA%20because%20of%20some%20leaders%20in%20the%20BJP.%20You%20split%20our%20party%20and%20gave%20what%20we%20were%20rightfully%20demanding%20to%20Eknath%20Shinde.%E2%80%9D%20Though%20no%20such%20discussions%20have%20taken%20place%20within%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20some%20members%20of%20the%20party%20might%20also%20share%20the%20same%20sentiments%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20doubt%20how%20long%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20will%20stay%20with%20the%20BJP.%20We%20are%20in%20a%20wait-and-watch%20mode%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20had%20such%20discussions%20several%20times%20earlier.%20However%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20talks%20in%20Sena%20(UBT)%20yet.%E2%80%9D%20The%20wedding%20reception%20of%20Alvani's%20daughter%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20leaders%20from%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%2C%20which%20comprises%20BJP%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20headed%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20and%20people%20from%20the%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20including%20filmmaker%20Madhur%20Bhandarkar%2C%20Shivaji%20Satam%20and%20Sachin%20Khedekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congressmen%20Kripashankar%20Singh%20and%20Krishna%20Hegde%2