0%26quot%3BThe%20engines%20rev%20up%2C%20and%20when%20they%20do%2C%20the%20pitch%20goes%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recommends%20having%20someone%20you%20feel%20safe%20around%2C%20like%20a%20partner%20or%20friend%2C%20hold%20neutral%20photographs%20of%20an%20airplane%20terminal%2C%20a%20plane%20in%20flight%2C%20and%20a%20plane%20landing%20to%20change%20your%20associations%20with%20the%20images.%20You%20can%20also%20picture%20them%20holding%20up%20the%20photographs%20while%20looking%20you%20in%20the%20eye%2C%20which%20can%20have%20a%20calming%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMenon%20also%20said%20exposure%20to%20more%20neutral%20images%20of%20planes%2C%20especially%20in%20contrast%20to%20distressing%20videos%20on%20social%20media%2C%20can%20help.%20If%20your%20fear%20of%20flying%20is%20severe%2C%20she%20recommended%20taking%20small%20steps%20like%20going%20with%20a%20loved%20one%20to%20an%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22085cacca-eb2a-4978-9fe2-4d907db69aae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEngage%20your%20senses%20when%20you're%20in%20the%20air%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you're%20on%20a%20flight%2C%20your%20options%20for%20calming%20down%20are%20more%20limited.%20Some%20techniques%20involve%20engaging%20your%20physical%20senses%20to%20pull%20away%20from%20ruminating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBunn%20suggested%20using%20the%2054321%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fgrounding-exercises%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrounding%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20you%20identify%20five%20things%20you%20can%20see%2C%20four%20things%20you%20can%20touch%2C%20three%20things%20you%20can%20hear%2C%20two%20things%20you%20can%20smell%2C%20and%20one%20thing%20you%20can%20taste.%20(Doing%20it%20in%20that%20order%20makes%20it%20harder%20for%20your%20brain%20to%20blow%20through%20the%20steps%20quickly%2C%20he%20said.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20anticipate%20being%20nervous%20on%20a%20flight%2C%20Menon%20said%20you%20can%20bring%20a%20tactile%20activity%20with%20you%2C%20such%20as%20crocheting%2C%20drawing%2C%20or%20playing%20with%20a%20fidget%20toy.%20%26quot%3BEngaging%20multiple%20senses%20allows%20us%20to%20anchor%20our%20minds%20and%20bodies%20into%20the%20present%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6f517b0-3fa2-4bdf-a5b8-5c9a46c2e031%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETry%20the%204-7-8%20breathing%20trick%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20simple%2C%20but%20breathing%20exercises%20work%20to%20quell%20your%20fears.%20Mindful%20breathing%20%26quot%3Bslows%20down%20our%20heart%20rate%20and%20triggers%20the%20relaxation%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20Menon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMenon%20recommended%20the%204-7-8%20breathing%20pattern%2C%20in%20which%20you%20inhale%20for%20four%20seconds%2C%20hold%20for%20seven%2C%20and%20exhale%20for%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBunn%20agreed.%20He%20said%20exhaling%20for%20longer%20than%20you%20inhale%20is%20his%20trick%20for%20calming%20the%20nervous%20system.%20He%20added%20that%20it%20may%20not%20be%20a%20perfect%20cure-all%2C%20especially%20in%20times%20of%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20plane%20drops%2C%20everybody's%20going%20to%20get%20some%20stress%20hormones%20released%2C%20some%20more%20than%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20this%20trick%2C%20Menon%20said%20it's%20best%20to%20do%20it%20a%20few%20times%20prior%20to%20boarding%20the%20aircraft%2C%20as%20well%20as%20when%20you%20just%20sat%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bad8fdc3-81bd-427d-ada5-ccd6c5968ee3%5C%22%3ELook%20at%20other%20stressors%20in%20your%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20suddenly%20developed%20aerophobia%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20Bunn%20said%20it%20could%20help%20to%20look%20at%20other%20stressors%20in%20your%20life%2C%20particularly%20ones%20that%20leave%20you%20feeling%20powerless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20%26quot%3Bstraws%20have%20been%20put%20on%20the%20camel's%20back%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20making%20you%20less%20tolerant%20of%20situations%20where%20you%20feel%20trapped%20%E2%80%94%20like%20being%20on%20a%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanage-flight-anxiety-expert-tips-to-ease-fear-of-flying-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738275892000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679be6087bb3f854015b3de0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanage-flight-anxiety-expert-tips-to-ease-fear-of-flying-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22High%20profile%20plane%20crashes%2C%20like%20the%20Washington%20DC%20crash%2C%20can%20heighten%20flight%20anxiety.%20Two%20aerophobia%20experts%20share%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20manage%20symptoms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanage-flight-anxiety-expert-tips-to-ease-fear-of-flying-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20FBI%20pick%20Kash%20Patel%20made%20more%20than%20%242.6%20million%20from%20consulting%2C%20paid%20speeches%2C%20and%20books%20last%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kash%20Patel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679bbcc8eb4be2fff9a2f27b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFBI%20Director%20nominee%20Kash%20Patel%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20%245.9%20million%20and%20made%20more%20than%20%242.6%20million%20last%20year.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Posner%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKash%20Patel%2C%20Trump's%20nominee%20to%20be%20FBI%20Director%2C%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20%245.9%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20made%20more%20than%20%242.6%20million%20last%20year%20from%20consulting%2C%20paid%20speeches%2C%20and%20books.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20clients%20included%20Truth%20Social%2C%20one%20of%20Trump's%20PACs%2C%20and%20the%20Embassy%20of%20Qatar.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-white-house-staff-cabinet-picks-list-2024-11%23kash-patel-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKash%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20nominee%20to%20be%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20made%20more%20than%20%242.6%20million%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs3.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25509708%2Fkash-patel-financial-disclosure.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20disclosure%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20ahead%20of%20its%20public%20release%2C%20Patel's%20income%20came%20from%20a%20mixture%20of%20consulting%20work%2C%20paid%20speeches%2C%20media%20appearances%2C%20and%20the%20proceeds%20of%20several%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20total%20net%20worth%20is%20more%20than%20%245.9%20million%2C%20according%20to%20a%20document%20filed%20with%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee.%20All%20of%20Trump's%20nominees%20are%20required%20to%20file%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-administration-nominee-financial-disclosures-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20final%20disclosure%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20are%20considered%20by%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20of%20Patel's%20income%2C%20more%20than%20%242.1%20million%2C%20came%20from%20consulting%20work.%20Among%20his%20clients%20was%20Trump%20Media%20and%20Technology%20Corp%2C%20the%20company%20that%20runs%20Truth%20Social.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1849635%2F000114036124030406%2Fny20026576x34_s1a.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20Patel's%20annual%20compensation%20was%20%24120%2C000%2C%20though%20his%20contract%20ended%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpam-bondi-truth-social-stock-lobbying-financial-disclosure-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPam%20Bondi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trump's%20nominee%20for%20attorney%20general%2C%20has%20also%20been%20financially%20tied%20up%20with%20Truth%20Social%2C%20holding%20more%20than%20%243.9%20million%20in%20stock%20in%20the%20company%20as%20of%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20also%20listed%20Save%20America%2C%20Trump's%20leadership%20PAC%2C%20as%20a%20client%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Embassy%20of%20Qatar%20and%20several%20other%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20earned%20%24306%2C000%20last%20year%20from%20a%20series%20of%20paid%20speeches%20and%20media%20appearances%2C%20including%20%2499%2C000%20for%20working%20as%20a%20contributor%20for%20the%20Epoch%20Times%20and%20%2420%2C000%20for%20a%20May%202024%20interview%20on%20%26quot%3BOur%20Watch%20With%20Tim%20Thompson.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriting%20books%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20lucrative%20for%20Patel.%20He%20earned%20between%20%24100%2C000%20and%20%241%20million%20in%20royalties%20for%20his%202023%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20Gangsters%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20between%20%2445%2C000%20and%20%24150%2C000%20for%20his%20%26quot%3BThe%20Plot%20Against%20the%20King%26quot%3B%20children's%20book%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20owns%20Elite%20Depot%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bfashion%20management%20company%26quot%3B%20based%20in%20the%20Cayman%20Islands%20worth%20between%20%241%20million%20and%20%245%20million.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Patel%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20regarding%20the%20organization's%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel's%20assets%20also%20include%20up%20to%20%24100%2C000%20in%20Bitcoin%2C%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%20in%20NVIDIA%20stock%2C%20and%20up%20to%20%24100%2C00%20in%20Palantir%20stock.%20In%202024%2C%20he%20earned%20%248%2C000%20in%20director's%20fees%20from%20VK%20Integrated%20Systems%2C%20a%20weapons%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20is%20among%20Trump's%20most%20controversial%20nominees%2C%20owing%20to%20questions%20about%20his%20conduct%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20his%20promotion%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20and%20his%20extreme%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20identified%20Patel%20this%20week%20as%20a%20nominee%20that%20Democrats%20felt%20they%20may%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20defeating.%20His%20first%20confirmation%20hearing%20took%20place%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20Patel's%20full%20financial%20disclosure%20below%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25509708-kash-patel-financial-disclosure%2F%3Fembed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fbi-director-kash-patel-financial-disclosure-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738275284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679bbcb77bb3f854015b2fef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fbi-director-kash-patel-financial-disclosure-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kash%20Patel%2C%20Trump's%20controversial%20pick%20to%20lead%20the%20FBI%2C%20dis