had%20Hodgkin's%20lymphoma%2C%20but%20she%20was%20lying.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20mom%20of%20two%20swindled%20over%20%24100%2C000%20from%20349%20donors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%202023%20podcast%20and%20a%20new%20docuseries%20explore%20%26quot%3BScamanda%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20fallout%20of%20Riley's%20fake%20cancer%20scheme.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20California-based%20Christian%20blogger%20and%20mother%20of%20two%20Amanda%20Christine%20Riley%20started%20%26quot%3BLymphoma%20Can%20Suck%20It%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flymphomacansuckit.blogspot.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esince-archived%20blog%3C%2Fa%3E%20documenting%20her%20journey%20after%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhank-green-shares-hodgkins-lymphoma-diagnosis-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHodgkin's%20lymphoma%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20her%20late%2020s.%20She%20used%20her%20blog%20and%20social%20media%20to%20publicize%20her%20journey%20with%20the%20aggressive%20form%20of%20cancer%2C%20winning%20over%20sympathy%20from%20friends%2C%20strangers%2C%20and%20even%20celebrities%20who%20gave%20her%20money%20for%20her%20medical%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20problem%3F%20Riley%20didn't%20have%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%2C%20now%2039%2C%20never%20had%20any%20cancer%20treatments%20because%20she%20never%20had%20the%20disease.%20And%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.truecrimedaily.com%2F2020%2F07%2F31%2Famanda-c-riley-1-complaint.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20criminal%20complaint%20filed%20by%20now-retired%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20%3C%2Fa%3E(IRS)%20special%20agent%20Arlette%20Lee%20in%20July%202020%2C%20she%20had%20used%20the%20ruse%20of%20the%20illness%20to%20bilk%20people%20out%20of%20over%20a%20total%20of%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20Charlie%20Webster's%20hit%202023%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flionsgatesound.com%2Fshows%2Fscamanda%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%20%26quot%3BScamanda%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20exposed%20the%20blogger's%20web%20of%20lies%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Riley's%20victims%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20law%20enforcement%20who%20worked%20the%20case.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20four-part%20ABC%20news%20docuseries%20of%20the%20same%20name%20premiering%20on%20January%2030%20delves%20further%20into%20how%20Riley%20pulled%20off%20her%20scheme%20and%20what%20ultimately%20gave%20her%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Lee's%20complaint%2C%20the%20former%20teacher%20and%20principal%20convinced%20friends%2C%20coworkers%2C%20a%20megachurch%2C%20and%20complete%20strangers%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleann-rimes-mental-health-celebrity-psoriasis-fame-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20singer%20LeAnn%20Rimes%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20donate%20over%20%24100%2C000%20to%20her%20and%20her%20family%20to%20help%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20her%20non-existent%20cancer%20treatments%20and%20travel%20for%20experiences%20she%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20have%20before%20she%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20shared%20on%20her%20blog%20multiple%20times%20that%20she%20was%20near%20death.%20But%20each%20time%2C%20she%20would%20experience%20a%20%26quot%3Bterminal%20miracle%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20inexplicably%20put%20her%20cancer%20into%20remission%2C%20taking%20her%20followers%20on%20an%20emotionally%20manipulative%20ride.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Riley%20even%20claimed%20that%20her%20pregnancy%20had%20%26quot%3Breversed%20the%20cancer.%26quot%3B%20(It%20would%20always%20eventually%20return.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20C.%20Riley%20with%20blonde%20hair%20and%20a%20Black%20shirt%20smiling.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d51c1648a88f0019691543%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERiley%20convinced%20LeAnn%20Rimes%20she%20had%20cancer.%3Cp%3ELionsgate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ndca%2Fpr%2Fwoman-formerly-bay-area-sentenced-five-years-prison-fraud-scheme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERiley%20collected%20at%20least%20349%20donations%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20eight%20years%20she%20perpetrated%20the%20fraud.%20They%20added%20up%20to%20more%20than%20%24105%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20where%20is%20Riley%20today%3F%20The%20end%20of%20her%20story%20isn't%20a%20miracle%2C%20but%20the%20consequences%20she%20faced%20are%20now%20a%20part%20of%20legal%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5cc7103-571f-4fe3-a3b0-70f1345e580d%5C%22%3EAmanda%20C.%20Riley%20faced%20repercussions%20for%20her%20fraud%20%E2%80%94%20and%20made%20legal%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drawing%20of%20Amanda%20C.%20Riley%20in%20court.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d51cd2005c4a00183d4fbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAccording%20to%20friends%20who%20appeared%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20Riley%20was%20telling%20lies%20up%20until%20her%202022%20sentencing.%3Cp%3ELionsgate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20wouldn't%20have%20happened%20without%20the%20work%20of%20investigative%20producer%20Nancy%20Moscatiello%2C%20who%20began%20an%20initial%20investigation%20into%20Riley%20after%20receiving%20an%20anonymous%20tip%20via%20email%20that%20she%20should%20look%20into%20the%20blogger%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20quickly%20went%20on%20the%20offensive%2C%20and%20attempted%20to%20sue%20Moscatiello%20for%20civil%20harassment%20(the%20judge%20threw%20out%20the%20suit).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoscatiello's%20own%20sister%20had%20died%20of%20cancer%2C%20and%20she%20dug%20in%2C%20calling%20the%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%20Riley%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20treated%20at%2C%20and%20closely%20examining%20the%20photos%20she%20posted%20on%20her%20blog.%20She%20took%20her%20findings%20to%20Jose%20Martinez%2C%20a%20now-retired%20San%20Jose-based%20financial%20crimes%20detective.%20Martinez%20contacted%20a%20facility%20where%20Riley%20claimed%20to%20be%20treated%3B%20an%20employee%20confirmed%20to%20him%20that%20Riley%20was%20not%20and%20had%20never%20been%20a%20patient%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartinez%2C%20realizing%20his%20scope%20was%20limited%20to%20San%20Jose%2C%20eventually%20passed%20the%20case%20on%20to%20the%20IRS%2C%20which%20had%20federal%20jurisdiction.%20IRS%20special%20agent%20Lee%20took%20the%20case%20over%20the%20line%2C%20subpoenaing%20every%20facility%20that%20Riley%20mentioned%20in%20her%20blog%20posts%20to%20establish%20that%20Riley%20didn't%20have%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20she%20was%20being%20actively%20investigated%20%E2%80%94%20investigators%20raided%20her%20house%20in%202016%20%E2%80%94%20Riley%20continued%20blogging%20and%20maintaining%20her%20claim%20she%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20cancer.%20She%20also%20took%20a%20job%20as%20a%20principal%20at%20Pacific%20Point%2C%20a%20Christian%20elementary%20school%2C%20and%20worked%20there%20for%20about%20three%20years%2C%20resigning%20just%20before%20federal%20authorities%20charged%20her%20with%20wire%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20charges%20were%20eventually%20brought%20against%20Riley%20in%20July%202020%2C%20related%20to%20financial%20crimes%20associated%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20scheme%20to%20solicit%20donations%20from%20individuals%20to%20help%20her%20pay%20for%20cancer%20treatments%20she%20never%20needed%20nor%20received%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DOJ%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20just%20how%20far%20Riley%20went%20to%20perpetrate%20the%20fraud%2C%20including%20shaving%20her%20head%20to%20appear%20as%20though%20she%20was%20receiving%20chemotherapy%2C%20falsifying%20medical%20records%2C%20forging%20physicians'%20documents%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20library%20of%20photos%20depicting%20her%20fake%20cancer%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20C.%20Riley%20smiling%20while%20waring%20a%20jean%20jacket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d51d9648a88f001969181c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20her%20conviction%2C%20Riley%20was%20the%20principal%20of%20a%20Christian%20elementary%20school.%3Cp%3ELionsgate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20wire%20fraud%20in%20October%202021%2C%20admitting%20in%20the%20written%20plea%20agreement%20that%20she%20knew%20she%20did%20not%20have%20Hodgkin's%20lymphoma%20and%20had%20never%20been%20diagnosed%20or%20treated%20with%20any%20type%20of%20cancer%2C%20and%20that%20she'd%20knowingly%20deceived%20people%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20give%20her%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20restitution%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20%24105%2C513%20and%20sentenced%20to%2060%20months%20in%20prison%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20made%20IRS%20history%20for%20being%20the%20first%20financial%20conviction%20of%20someone%20who%20faked%20cancer%20for%20fundraising%20purposes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BScamanda%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20is%20incarcerated%20at%20FMC%20Carswell%2C%20a%20federal%20prison%20in%20Ft.%20Worth%2C%20Texas%2C%20that%20houses%20prisoners%20at%20all%20security%20levels%20and%20specializes%20in%20p