%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECurie's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74627-20%26h%3D168d1ada3fbe48dcb2b3b9c88ce0c9556e48f8f2df60cbfb548ed79c7775eea9%26postID%3D679bd022e72cf8b493652e36%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fcurie-deodorant-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fcuriebod.com%25252Fproducts%25252Faluminum-free-deodorant-spray%25253Fvariant%25253D31625682911310%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espray%20deodorant%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20so%20much%20better%20than%20any%20other%20natural%20or%20aluminum-free%20options%20I've%20tried.%20Most%20formulas%20have%20left%20my%20underarm%20skin%20feeling%20irritated%2C%20and%20none%20have%20actually%20curbed%20odor%20(some%20have%20even%20made%20me%20smell%20worse).%20But%20Curie's%20spray%20keeps%20me%20feeling%20fresh%20even%20after%20emerging%20covered%20in%20sweat%20from%20a%20super%20intense%20spin%20class.%20The%20more%20I%20used%20it%2C%20the%20more%20I%20recognized%20that%20it%20wasn't%20a%20fluke%20%E2%80%94%20it%20worked%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20well%20for%20me.%20Now%2C%20I%20just%20spray%20it%20on%20every%20morning%2C%20let%20my%20pits%20dry%20before%20I%20get%20dressed%2C%20and%20go%20about%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0275e7c-f6f9-4f26-ad3b-a3fe4913c29f%5C%22%3EIt%20doesn't%20reduce%20sweat%20as%20much%20as%20an%20antiperspirant%2C%20but%20it%20does%20control%20odor%20extremely%20well.%20I%20asked%20a%20dermatologist%20to%20explain%20why.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20prevent%20sweating%20is%20to%20use%20an%20aluminum-based%20deodorant%20(aka%20an%20antiperspirant)%2C%20which%20essentially%20clogs%20sweat%20glands%20to%20prevent%20sweating.%20Most%20people%20think%20natural%20or%20aluminum-free%20deodorants%20aren't%20as%20effective%20as%20aluminum-based%20antiperspirants%2C%20but%20they're%20technically%20different%20products%20with%20different%20functionalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcuriebod.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECurie's%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20deodorants%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20they're%20primarily%20designed%20to%20keep%20you%20from%20smelling%20gross%2C%20but%20the%20spray%20does%20have%20some%20element%20of%20sweat%20prevention.%20I%20asked%20cosmetic%20dermatologist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dermatologist-nyc.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Debra%20Jaliman%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20ingredients%20used%20in%20the%20spray%2C%20and%20she%20explained%20that%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20ingredients%2C%20witch%20hazel%2C%20is%20an%20astringent%20that%20can%20reduce%20sweat%20and%20odor.%20She%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20probiotics%20like%20saccharomyces%20ferment%20and%20lactobacillus%20ferment%20can%20help%20to%20balance%20the%20skin's%20microbiome%20and%20decrease%20surface%20bacteria%20(the%20stuff%20that%20makes%20you%20stink).%20Lastly%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20triethyl%20citrate%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20prevent%20the%20breakdown%20of%20sweat%20into%20odor-causing%20compounds%2C%20so%20it%20decreases%20odor%20from%20underarm%20sweat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239bf2f36-7831-4056-9c28-41907a9b452a%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20a%20ton%20of%20fragrance%20options%20for%20every%20kind%20of%20preference.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20Orange%20Neroli%20and%20Grapefruit%20Cassis%20scents%2C%20but%20the%20White%20Tea%20is%20also%20a%20fan%20favorite.%20There%20are%20several%20other%20options%2C%20like%20coconut%2C%20vanilla%2C%20eucalyptus%2C%20and%20peach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fellow%20editor%2C%20Maiya%20Pascouche%2C%20tested%20out%20the%20Peach%20Soleil%20scent%20and%20wasn't%20a%20big%20fan%2C%20so%20the%20fragrances%20can%20be%20hit%20or%20miss%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20they%20just%20don't%20mix%20well%20with%20your%20body%20chemistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222beef1fe-d567-4a7a-90f5-015c7e807c8d%5C%22%3ECurie%20has%20several%20other%20products%2C%20including%20a%20stick%20version%20of%20their%20deodorant%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20prefer%20the%20spray.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holds%20two%20bottles%20of%20Curie%20Stick%20Deodorant%20and%20Dry%20Shampoo%20in%20their%20hand%20against%20a%20green-patterned%20bathroom%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679bd738eb4be2fff9a2f941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECurie%20started%20with%20a%20stick%20formula%20first%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20say%2C%20it's%20not%20my%20favorite.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20baking%20soda%20in%20the%20stick%20version%20is%20slightly%20irritating%20to%20my%20skin%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20find%20that%20it%20helped%20with%20odor%20control%20(even%20after%20testing%20multiple%20fragrances).%20The%20arrowroot%20starch%20in%20the%20formula%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20absorbing%20moisture%2C%20but%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20stick%20just%20doesn't%20control%20odor%20quite%20as%20well%20as%20the%20spray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20find%20products%20like%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74627-20%26h%3Df146626900c43ff760582a31255070fc0590397c9f32b55220708469c1bccf44%26postID%3D679bd022e72cf8b493652e36%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fcurie-deodorant-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fcuriebod.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fclay-detox-mask%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earmpit%20detox%20mask%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%