ian%20to%20go%20to%20space%20after%20Wing%20Commander%20Rakesh%20Sharma's%20journey%20on%20board%20the%20Soyuz%20T-11%20in%20April%201984%2C%20will%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20pilot%20on%20the%20Axiom%20Mission%204%2C%20or%20Ax-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ax-4%20will%20go%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20from%20the%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration's%20(NASA)%20Kennedy%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Florida%20no%20earlier%20than%20spring%202025%2C%20Axiom%20told%20reporters%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20Captain%20Shukla%2C%20who%20is%20serving%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%2C%20has%20also%20been%20chosen%20as%20an%20astronaut%20for%20India's%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%20It%20was%20ISRO%20that%20sent%20him%20to%20NASA%20for%20the%20Ax-4%20mission%20to%20the%20ISS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeggy%20Whitson%2C%20former%20NASA%20astronaut%20and%20director%20of%20human%20spaceflight%20at%20Axiom%20Space%2C%20will%20command%20the%20private%20Ax-4%20mission%2C%20while%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20will%20serve%20as%20pilot%2C%20the%20American%20space%20agency%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20really%20excited%20to%20go%20into%20microgravity%20and%20experience%20space%20flight%20on%20my%20own.%20The%20tempo%20for%20the%20mission%20has%20been%20building%20up%20each%20month.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20at%20a%20stage%20wherein%20all%20the%20pieces%20are%20kind%20of%20coming%20together.%20I'm%20extremely%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20this%20unfolds%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20for%20the%20actual%20space%20flight%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fvmfklp7o_axiom-4_62