ect.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Freturn-to-the-ruins-thousands-of-displaced-palestinians-return-to-devastation-amid-israel-hamas-ceasefire%2Famp_etphotostory%2F117750153.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Freturn-to-the-ruins-thousands-of-displaced-palestinians-return-to-devastation-amid-israel-hamas-ceasefire%2Famp_etphotostory%2F117750153.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Blames%20%26quot%3BDiversity%20Policies%26quot%3B%20Under%20Obama%2C%20Biden%20After%20Chopper-Plane%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20blamed%20diversity%20policies%20implemented%20during%20the%20Obama%20and%20Biden%20administrations%20for%20compromising%20air%20safety%20standards.%20This%20statement%20came%20after%20a%20devastating%20mid-air%20collision%20between%20an%20American%20Airlines%20passenger%20jet%20and%20a%20US%20Army%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter%2C%20resulting%20in%20no%20survivors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20remarks%20have%20ignited%20a%20heated%20debate%20about%20the%20role%20of%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20(DEI)%20programs%20in%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA).%20The%20President%20claimed%20that%20these%20initiatives%20prioritised%20policy%20over%20safety%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20put%20safety%20first.%20Obama%2C%20Biden%2C%20and%20the%20Democrats%20put%20policy%20first.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20emphasised%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20actually%20came%20out%20with%20a%20directive%3A%20'too%20white.'%20And%20we%20want%20the%20people%20that%20are%20competent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA's%20hiring%20practices%20have%20been%20under%20scrutiny%2C%20with%20some%20critics%20arguing%20that%20DEI%20programs%20can%20be%20discriminatory.%20However%2C%20supporters%20of%20these%20initiatives%20contend%20that%20they%20address%20historical%20and%20ongoing%20discrimination%20against%20underrepresented%20groups%2C%20including%20racial%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20specifically%20targeted%20former%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Pete%20Buttigieg%2C%20implying%20that%20he%20hired%20unqualified%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%20and%20psychological%20issues%20for%20air%20traffic%20control%20positions.%20Trump%20expressed%20his%20doubts%20about%20their%20competence%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20so.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20FAA%20was%20%26quot%3Bran%20into%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20by%20DEI%20hires%20after%20being%20deemed%20%26quot%3Btoo%20white%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20crash%2C%20Trump%20is%20appointing%20Chris%20Rocheleau%20as%20the%20acting%20administrator%20of%20the%20FAA.%20The%20agency's%20hiring%20practices%20and%20safety%20standards%20will%20likely%20face%20intense%20scrutiny%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20changes%20to%20the%20FAA's%20hiring%20practices%20were%20made%20during%20the%20Obama%20administration%2C%20which%20introduced%20a%20biographical%20test%20as%20part%20of%20the%20application%20process.%20This%20move%20aimed%20to%20increase%20diversity%20among%20air%20traffic%20controllers.%20However%2C%20some%20have%20criticised%20this%20approach%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20prioritised%20diversity%20over%20competence.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738256700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fkoorlil_donald-trump-afp_625x300_30_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-blames-diversity-policies-under-obama-biden-after-chopper-plane-crash-7597931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20remarks%20have%20ignited%20a%20heated%20debate%20about%20the%20role%20of%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20(DEI)%20programs%20in%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUr